# Athena-Orchestrator scratch: PLAN.md is the orchestrator's dispatch
# queue (see CLAUDE.md "PLAN.md format contract"), TODO/STATUS are
# operator-facing notes. All three carry internal task metadata and are
# not part of the public product surface, so we untrack them at the
# root — the orchestrator still finds PLAN.md via the filesystem path.
/PLAN.md
/TODO.md
/STATUS.md

